     2	
     3	Full `lite` / `standard` / `strict` presets for the 24 leaf fields of `control-contract-template.md`. `$harnessloop-setup` step S4 shows the summary below, asks the user to pick one with `AskUserQuestion`, builds a diff of the current `state/control-contract.md` against the selected profile's full content, and writes it only after the user sees that diff. Re-selecting a profile later — including switching from one profile to another — follows the same diff-and-confirm flow; it never silently overwrites.
     4	
