    62	## How `$harnessloop-setup` Applies A Profile
    63	
    64	1. Read the current `state/control-contract.md` (template, or a previously applied profile).
    65	2. Ask which profile to apply with `AskUserQuestion`: `lite` / `standard` / `strict`.
